profile.headline: Senior Software Engineer at GitLab
profile.summary: Highly motivated and experienced software engineer with a passion for open-source development, leveraging expertise in Java and road-runner to drive innovation.

experience.title: Senior Software Engineer
description: Developed and maintained multiple high-performance applications using Java and road-runner, ensuring scalability and reliability in a remote work environment.
Collaborated with cross-functional teams to design and implement new features, resulting in improved user experience and increased productivity.
Continuously contributed to the growth of open-source projects, including FTC Android Studio and road-runner quickstarts.

experience.title: Freelance Developer
description: Developed custom applications for clients across various industries, utilizing Java and Android Studio to deliver high-quality solutions.
Maintained multiple open-source repositories on GitHub, including FTC Android Studio projects and road-runner quickstarts.

experience.title: Open Source Maintainer
description: Contributed to the development and maintenance of the FTC Android Studio project, ensuring its continued growth and adoption in the robotics community.
Participated in regular code reviews and provided feedback to improve the overall quality and stability of the project.
